<document> 

  <properties>
    <title>Expression step</title>
    <author email="jourdren@biologie.ens.fr">Laurent Jourdren</author> 
  </properties> 



  <body>
  
    <section name="Expression step">

      <p>This step allow to compute expression using the filtered alignments and a annotation file that contains genomic elements to count.</p>  

      <ul>
         <li><b>Name</b>: expression.</li>
         <li><b>Available</b>: Both local and distributed mode.</li>
        <li><b>Input</b>: filtered alignments (e.g. <code>filtered_mapper_results_1.sam</code>).</li>
        <li><b>Output</b>: expression file (e.g. <code>expression_1.txt</code>).</li>
	 <br/>
         <li><b>Parameters</b>:</li>
	<table>
		<tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Value</th><th>Description</th></tr>
		<tr><td>genomictype</td><td>string</td><td>Genomic elements of the annotation file to count.</td></tr>
	</table>
       </ul>
      
	<p>In local mode, use the <b>main.tmp.dir</b> global parameter to set the temporary directory if this step fails with a full disk error.</p>

    </section>


  </body>
  
</document>
